{"id": 1700, "genre": 1000, "title": "哪些家居设计不合理不舒适，但你还是凑合地忍着？", "description": "你还有哪些居家难题，欢迎留言补充。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 12062, "comment_count": 27, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170523143600dBTHMrbPYSJqZm97.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-23T17:00:56Z", "questions": [{"id": 2348, "title": "哪些家居设计不合理不舒适，但你还是凑合地忍着？", "content": "哪些家居设计不合理不舒适，但你还是凑合地忍着？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 206629, "content": "储物：没有足够的储物空间，东西只好堆在各个地方", "image": "img/option/option/20170523144158Xxz2J9d6rmP3Zycs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 206630, "content": "插座：太少或太低，我的手机天天躺在地上充电", "image": "img/option/option/201705231441485ZanUlsvzb47TX3P.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 206631, "content": "没有玄关：一进门只能把衣服和包扔在沙发上", "image": "img/option/option/20170523144547KI46mHMhCoJDfztG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 206632, "content": "厨房：厨房台面太小，水槽太窄，油烟机太差", "image": "img/option/option/20170523150027n7yx0LfiWgumsRtb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 206633, "content": "开关：太多太乱，一整排不知道哪个开关对哪个灯", "image": "img/option/option/20170523150640k0f6rU29mpeoZsId.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 206634, "content": "距离：卧室开关离床太远，睡前总要下床去关灯", "image": "img/option/option/201705231510479DVNA4PObl3WLm65.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 206636, "content": "位置问题：水龙头位置太低，橱柜位置太高", "image": "img/option/option/20170523151611JmHCgU5whpAYbSk9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 206637, "content": "细节：洗脸池太浅，淋浴门不密闭", "image": "img/option/option/20170523151817sqznBZy2eDJvj75N.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 206638, "content": "难清洁：沙发套不能拆洗，敞开式书柜积灰", "image": "img/option/option/20170523152113uGoXax1FP8rpgKNl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}